{"tid":1496900,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文革前毛澤東鼓勵市民表達意見，批評都唔緊要","createTime":"2019-08-22T17:13:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T18:52:31.000Z","uid":58841,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"850fff5580592b399988ff45856772865d9134f3","tid":1496900,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:13:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結果文化大革命呢班人全部被批鬥而死<br />\n傷亡達4000萬<br />\n去讀下近代史<br />\n支那講既野係一句都唔信得</span></span>"},{"pid":"624f9e03bfd4d14748f58ec7ac237d0fe820f7ed","tid":1496900,"uid":58841,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"64前夕<br />\n李鵬趁趙紫陽離開同學生對話<br />\n對話完即刻清場<br />\n鄧小平睇到傷亡人數之後講既係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">吓？乜殺得咁少人炸</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而趙紫陽相當後悔阻止唔到學生<br />\n落台之後被軟禁"},{"pid":"a570b2f240d045c4863d4b742222a39c3563b0f1","tid":1496900,"uid":58841,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"趙紫陽原本係國民黨既人<br />\n1989年的六四事件中，趙紫陽因公開表示同情學生和反對武力鎮壓，而招致鄧小平、陳雲、李先念和李鵬等人的不滿，被免去黨內外一切領導職務，最終在軟禁中度過了生命中最後的16年，於2005年逝世<br />\n<br />\n岩岩睇到個post話有fd收到電話話邀請對話<br />\n我想講去左唔單止俾手足當係鬼<br />\n你仲行左條死路"},{"pid":"ccb586299092f843511f212f742398033b82e24b","tid":1496900,"uid":250580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:24:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d56106dbba5ff83ee2e97d70d17e27d5851934fa","tid":1496900,"uid":61611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:25:37.000Z","msg":"比你寫大字報屌政府<br />\n之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22286591f051d0fc8df79ed78cea1733debf13e4","tid":1496900,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"而家已經清算梗，睇下國泰"},{"pid":"757a96ab268ab779d4e3c16ab500cadb06fec91a","tid":1496900,"uid":13090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17: